Model    Type              Best For...                         """Vibe"""
SARIMA   Statistical       Quarterly patterns & short-term.    Precise & Rigid
ETS      Statistical       Stable, long-term trends.           Smooth & Reliable
Prophet  Decomposable      Messy data & "Holiday" effects.     User-friendly
XGBoost  Machine Learning  Using many external indicators.     Powerful & Complex
Theta    Hybrid            Long-range, noisy data.             Simple & Robust
